{"tid":580754,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友 我好掛住你","createTime":"2018-03-04T18:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T23:26:31.000Z","uid":145618,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b5b08a53f03bd6aa36b380cc7a174c86f326cc50","tid":580754,"uid":145618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:03:02.000Z","msg":"最好既朋友一句野都冇講低就自殺 係由細玩到大果種<br />\n然後我每晚一合埋眼就諗起佢<br />\n邊諗到好兄弟就咁就走左 好想係假<br />\n一起身 當真係發覺佢真係唔係到既時候<br />\n果種感覺真係好傷心 同一時間覺得自己好冇用<br />\n救佢唔到 <br />\n有排好唔開心 屋企令我好大壓力 大到想自殺<br />\n係佢同另一個朋友拉住我先冇死<br />\n但到佢有事 我竟然拉佢唔住 <br />\n<br />\n我真係好掛住你 兄弟"},{"pid":"c417c1d486ebc90d09c9a6833cc693f943292f56","tid":580754,"uid":66436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:03:52.000Z","msg":"酩酊天使 聽下"},{"pid":"e3b1236737fd0e9a651b69614bbff8625c5cfcc9","tid":580754,"uid":130040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:06:42.000Z","msg":"加油 好好活下去"},{"pid":"bce9ef084e2e4f10f285cee297748a70619c9e1d","tid":580754,"uid":44807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:07:42.000Z","msg":"巴打幾大，有時我都會諗自己兄弟過身會點。結果係我都會知自己會崩潰。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385d6b78f25b381e92efb803b12dc228d06bc77d","tid":580754,"uid":45933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:31:36.000Z","msg":"聽下不求人啦ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d490997d8bec14381712ba143e181ff155c1ff92","tid":580754,"uid":145618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bce9ef084e2e4f10f285cee297748a70619c9e1d","tid":580754,"uid":44807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T18:07:42.000Z","msg":"巴打幾大，有時我都會諗自己兄弟過身會點。結果係我都會知自己會崩潰。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T23:24:56.000Z","msg":"21冇耐 冇左佢 世界就好似小左啲野 冇曬真正既情緒"},{"pid":"372ceddb92b9a3b1ae129e47f2d55211aeeb1a22","tid":580754,"uid":145618,"l